msgid "Brightness level"
msgstr "Helderheidsniveau"

#. Setting help text
msgctxt "#30001"
msgid "Level in percent of how strongly the screen remains illuminated."
msgstr "Niveau in procent van hoe sterk het scherm verlicht blijft."

